summary: im looking for this taegi fic where taehyung and yoongi see each other only once a year for a while and then they meet again...
question: im looking for this taegi fic where taehyung and yoongi see each other only once a year for a while and then they meet again after a few years in a airport after yoongi ghosted him? the flight also gets canceled and they have to share a hotel room?
answer:
this one?

All Eternal Things by bowandarrow

This is how they first met, and it’s how they’ve always been. They orbit around each other like distant planets for months until this godforsaken holiday rolls around, and they always, always align.

Or the one where Taehyung and Yoongi are childhood friends who always travel home together for Lunar New Year.

summary: I’m sure some of you are in the same boat as me and could use some more friends. I’m a bit shy but feel free to message me...
body:
In desperate need of friends.

I’m sure some of you are in the same boat as me and could use some more friends. I’m a bit shy but feel free to message me anytime, I always reply and follow everyone back. Other social media I have is KakaoTalk, Twitter, Snapchat, Instagram, Facebook, and Line. Or we could even be penpals- I have some really cute stationary to use.

Some things about myself: I’m turning 21 in a month, I’m bi,(update March 26:just realized I’m a lesbian) I have a super sweet and clingy cat that I’ll share pictures of. My favorite bands are BTS (I have a huge collection) and Chase Atlantic (I’m met them several times and they are sweet hearts). 

I’m really open minded so if we become friends if there’s anything you’re a fan of, I’ll definitely look into/watch/read/listen to it so that way you can fangirl/fanboy with me.
